title: Quadro Nuevo - Tango Bitter Sweet [FLAC] + covers
description:
Very good mix of old and new things in soft & warm performance. Excellent disk for quiet  evening with glass of whisky ;) 
I think it was one of the best disks of last year. More info about Quadro Nuevo on http://www.quadronuevo.de/
 "The group performs a good variety of quintessentially European compositions, nearly half of which were written by members of the quartet....With TANGO BITTER SWEET, Quadro Nuevo proves once again to be a class act worthy of the notices it has received."
                                                                   Global Rhythm

All pictures in booklet is 300 pixels/inch. All tracks are separate & with tags. Ripped by EAC.
If you want to burn this CD, you can download cole2K nero audio plugin (google helps you), or use alcohol, EAC  etc.
